{"title":"歌唱大丰收","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱大丰收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河两岸好风光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野里的麦子赛金黄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹麦浪散芳香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日照麦粒放光芒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍珠穗儿肥又大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩能产千斤粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关心咱们像爹娘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导俺们修水利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驯服淮河万民康；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去的水浪变麦浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不毛之地变粮仓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水永不欺侮俺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少喜洋洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——淮滨县　李荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铲麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年麦子真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片黄金随风摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘来到地头上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您大个子没麦高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光油油铲杆八尺长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安张铲刀闪银光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘挽袖把麦铲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手一推丈把长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦棵倒地一尺深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地飞起黄灰尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"额上汗珠一串串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶赤日脚踩云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“前面大嫂快快铲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢了小心脚后跟！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得大嫂把话答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱可都得安好心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要心眼不安正，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫她找不到好爱人！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——扶沟　张成美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦车装得像金山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压得车辕打颤颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三套红骡把车拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累得浑身淌热汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伯哼着丰收歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路响鞭甩个欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——洛阳杜村乡　张石滚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骡子卸下磙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日头落西山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员来扬场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里掂木?。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚风刮的欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像风车扇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦糠遮红霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦籽似雨点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙赤着臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘把袖挽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木?上下飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看谁干的欢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘了脖子疼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘了胳膊酸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看麦场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金山长上天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——洛阳杜村乡　张石滚"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1}